# Build System

- **Generator:** Ninja (`cmake -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug`).
- **ccache:** auto-detected by CMake; keep installed for faster rebuilds.
- **Outputs:** all build artifacts go in `build/`.

## New targets

Every new library/executable must include PCH:

```cmake
target_precompile_headers(<target_name> PRIVATE ${PROJECT_PCH_HEADERS})
```

Test targets use `${TEST_PCH_HEADERS}`.

## Practices

- Prefer forward declarations in headers to reduce include depth.
- Unity builds optional: `-DENABLE_UNITY_BUILD=ON/OFF`.
- Merge SQL migrations: `cmake --build build --target merge-migrations`.

Details: `.agent/skills/Optimization/SKILL.md` and `AGENTS.md`.
